headline: Two Veterans Will Soon Receive Life-Saving Service Dogs Thanks to Petsense by Tractor Supply’s Round-Up Campaign
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., November 13, 2025--Petsense by Tractor Supply, a wholly owned subsidiary of Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), has raised over $130,000 across 206 stores nationwide for K9s For Warriors, the nation’s leading service dog program for veterans. The donation will directly fund the training and pairing of two life-saving service dogs for veterans with PTSD and other invisible wounds of war.
